"2 tablespoons salted butter","1/4 cup finely chopped yellow onion","2 teaspoons minced garlic","4 1/2 cups water","1 teaspoon table salt","1 1/2 cups uncooked yellow stone-ground grits","2  (8-oz.) pkg. cubed boneless ham, drained and patted dry with paper towels","1  (8-oz.) pkg. shredded sharp Cheddar cheese","1  (8-oz.) pkg. shredded extra-sharp Cheddar cheese","1 cup whole milk","1 cup fresh corn kernels (from about 2 ears)","1 1/2 teaspoons chopped fresh thyme","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","4  large eggs, lightly beaten"